vernac_cmds: Structure embedding (I J : interp domain eta) := { Hf : forall b d, @i_f _ _ I b d = @i_f _ _ J b d ; He : @i_e _ _ I = @i_e _ _ J ; HP : forall c d, @i_P _ _ I c d -> @i_P _ _ J c d ; HQ : @i_Q _ _ I -> @i_Q _ _ J }.
Lemma emb_refl (I : interp domain eta) : embedding I I.
Definition emb_trans (I J K : interp domain eta) : embedding I J -> embedding J K -> embedding I K.

Class kmodel := { nodes : Type ; reachable : nodes -> nodes -> Prop ; reach_refl u : reachable u u ; reach_tran u v w : reachable u v -> reachable v w -> reachable u w ; world : nodes -> interp domain eta ; world_f : forall u v, reachable u v -> embedding (world u) (world v) }.

Fixpoint ksat b u (rho : var -> domain) (phi : form b) : Prop := match phi with | Pr t1 t2 => @i_P _ _ (world u) (@eval _ _ (world u) rho t1) (@eval _ _ (world u) rho t2) | Q => @i_Q _ _ (world u) | Fal => False | Impl phi psi => forall v, reachable u v -> ksat v rho phi -> ksat v rho psi | All n phi => forall v, reachable u v -> forall j : domain, ksat v (rho [[ n := j ]]) phi end.
Notation "rho '⊨(' u ')' phi" := (ksat u rho phi) (at level 20).
Notation "rho '⊫(' u ')' A" := (forall phi, phi el A -> rho ⊨(u) phi) (at level 20).
Lemma eval_invar u v : reachable u v -> forall rho t, @eval _ _ (world u) rho t = @eval _ _ (world v)rho t.
Lemma ksat_mon b (u : nodes) (rho : var -> domain) (phi : form b) : forall v (H : reachable u v), ksat u rho phi -> ksat v rho phi.
induction phi; intros rho v H; cbn.
Lemma ksat_iff b u rho phi : ksat u rho phi <-> forall v (H : reachable u v), ksat v rho phi.
Notation sem_imp v rho A phi := ((forall psi, psi el A -> ksat v rho psi) -> ksat v rho phi).
Lemma impl_ksat {b} u A rho (phi : form b) : ksat u rho (A ==> phi) <-> (forall v, reachable u v -> sem_imp v rho A phi).
induction A; cbn; intros u rho.
split; intros H v H1 H2.
assert (H' : ksat v rho a) by (now apply H2; now left).
Lemma impl_ksat' {b} u A rho (phi : form b) : ksat u rho (A ==> phi) -> (forall v, reachable u v -> sem_imp v rho A phi).
Notation "rho '⊩(' u , M , eta ')' phi" := (@ksat _ eta M _ u rho phi) (at level 20).
Instance interp_kripke {domain eta} (I : interp domain eta) : kmodel eta := {| nodes := unit ; reachable u v := True |}.
Lemma kripke_tarski domain eta (b : logic) (I : interp domain eta) rho phi : rho ⊨ phi <-> rho ⊩(tt, interp_kripke I, _) phi.
apply IHphi2, (H tt Logic.I), IHphi1, H'.
Definition kvalid b (phi : form b) := forall domain eta (M : @kmodel domain eta) u rho, rho ⊩(u,M,eta) phi.
Definition ksatis b (phi : form b) := exists domain eta (M : @kmodel domain eta) u rho, ksat eta M u rho phi.
Lemma kvalid_valid b (phi : form b) : kvalid phi -> valid phi.
intros H domain I eta rho.
Lemma ksatis_satis b (phi : form b) : satis phi -> ksatis phi.
now exists domain, eta, (interp_kripke I), tt, rho.
Definition kcast domain (eta eta' : nat -> domain) (M : kmodel eta) : kmodel eta'.
abstract ( intros; cbn; destruct (world_f0 u v H), (world0 u), (world0 v); cbn; econstructor; eauto).

Lemma ksat_ext_p dom b (phi : form b) rho rho' eta eta' (M : @kmodel dom eta ) u : (forall v, rho v = rho' v) -> (forall p, p el consts phi -> eta p = eta' p) -> rho ⊩(u,M,eta) phi <-> rho' ⊩(u, !M, eta') phi.
revert u rho rho' H; induction phi; cbn in *; intros.
Lemma ksat_ext dom b (phi : form b) rho rho' eta (M : @kmodel dom eta ) u : rho ⊩(u,M,eta) phi -> (forall v, rho v = rho' v) -> rho' ⊩(u,M,eta) phi.
Lemma subst_ksat dom b eta rho (M : @kmodel dom eta ) u (phi : form b) x t : vars_t t = [] -> rho ⊩(u,M,eta) (subst x t phi) <-> rho[[x:=eval (I:=world u) rho t]] ⊩(u,M,eta) phi.
induction phi; intros u rho; cbn in *; try rewrite fresh_app in *.
split; intros H w H1 H2.
rewrite eval_empty with (rho':=rho) in H; trivial.

Lemma substconst_ksat b dom eta rho (phi : form b) x a d (M : @kmodel dom eta) u : fresh a (consts phi) -> rho ⊩(u, kcast (eta [[a := d]]) M, _) (subst x (P a) phi) <-> rho [[ x := d ]] ⊩(u,M,eta) phi.
eapply ksat_ext_p; intros n; repeat decs.
Lemma ksoundness' {b} A (phi : form b) : A ⊢I phi -> kvalid (A ==> phi).
induction 1; intros domain eta M u rho; eapply impl_ksat; intros; subst.
apply (impl_ksat' (IHprv eq_refl domain eta M u rho) ).
pose proof (impl_ksat' (IHprv1 eq_refl domain eta M u rho)).
eapply (impl_ksat' (IHprv2 eq_refl domain eta M u rho)); eauto.
specialize (IHprv eq_refl domain _ (kcast (eta [[y := d]]) M) w rho).
pose proof (impl_ksat' (IHprv eq_refl domain eta M u rho)).
specialize (IHprv eq_refl domain eta M v rho).
eapply impl_ksat in IHprv as []; eauto.
Theorem ksoundness {b} (phi : form b) : [] ⊢I phi -> valid phi.

command: induction phi; intros rho v H; cbn.
induction A; cbn; intros u rho.
split; intros H v H1 H2.
assert (H' : ksat v rho a) by (now apply H2; now left).
apply IHphi2, (H tt Logic.I), IHphi1, H'.
intros H domain I eta rho.
now exists domain, eta, (interp_kripke I), tt, rho.
induction phi; intros u rho; cbn in *; try rewrite fresh_app in *.
split; intros H w H1 H2.
rewrite eval_empty with (rho':=rho) in H; trivial.
eapply ksat_ext_p; intros n; repeat decs.
